title: Rob Zombie's Halloween, Vol. 1: The Ascension of Fear
description:
[img]http://i.imgur.com/nV5SxNG.jpg[/img]

This is the first part of an updated version of my original three hour fan edit of the Rob Zombie Halloween movies, split back into two movies.

With the exception of various deleted scenes reinstated into the film, all sources used in this edit were in high definition, including the much sought-after "theatrical cut" version of Michael's escape.

"Vol. 2: The Downfall of Innocence" to be released at a later date
